{
  "stem": "13833.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was another lady-- there was a German woman who was married to a Swede with two little boys.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was the famous vitamin-- the Nobel Prize-winning vitamin-- Szent-Gyorgyi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if you heard his name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was there with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he had to be removed after, with another face and name, because the Germans knew that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were after him because he was a great anti-Nazi Christian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- the danger for my parents, because I wasn't in danger anymore.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my parents were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then my parents were so happy that I lived and that they will take care.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, of course, every day, the diplomat went down to my parents to see if they're all right.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were still in the Christian house then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then the bombing started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was the day one American was shot down and fell into the Danube.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we saw it from where we were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because we were on the Buda side and the German headquarters were behind us, shooting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that poor guy fell into the water with a parachute.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took him out and lynched him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then the Jews have to be dying and the Arrow Cross said that every second house they're going to make a Jewish house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So in Budapest, every second house had a big Magen David.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because, they said, now the Allied forces won't bomb Budapest because they think they will kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How stupid can they be?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From up there, they can't see which one was a Jewish house and which one is a Christian house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the, the Jewish people have to get out of the Christian house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my parents had to move.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
